    },
    {
      "id": "beee0fde-6bbd-47a5-8212-c23289463eee",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Antes tinha medo do tal João do Santo Cristo, era o que todos diziam quando ele se perdeu",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 6.86,
      "timestamp_end": 9.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:45:45.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:45:48.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "6697f8b9-3c56-433c-9450-e8b7bad6d844",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Fechou o padrastro do marado da fazenda só pra sentir no seu sangue o ódio que Jesus lhe deu",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 9.86,
      "timestamp_end": 12.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:45:48.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:45:51.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "296f8095-98aa-4f31-bd63-a942b1ce1fc1",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Quando o fião sobe, sabe ser bandido ainda mais do que um tiro do soldado pra correr",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 12.86,
      "timestamp_end": 15.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:45:51.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:45:54.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "1bf5f342-a69b-4982-8d77-e760fdf50159",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "É no terror da cercaninha onde morava na escola, até o professor com ele ia aprender",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 15.86,
      "timestamp_end": 18.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:45:54.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:45:57.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "0fe50a7e-72a6-42f3-84d1-5974b894da36",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Ia pra greve só pra roubar no dinheiro, peça que não se colocava na caixinha de volta",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 18.86,
      "timestamp_end": 20.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:45:57.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:45:59.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "1a727017-14ad-41d7-942a-f8f3ff257d45",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Sentia mesmo que era mesmo de bem, sentia que o alião era o seu lugar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 20.86,
      "timestamp_end": 23.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:45:59.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:02.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "cc85309c-4315-47c0-bb3e-96ba90fc0cc9",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Ele queria sair para ver o mar, as coisas que ele via na televisão",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 23.86,
      "timestamp_end": 26.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:46:02.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:05.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "7a5ec807-3c83-44d2-8681-4f47a1d2319f",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Juntou o dinheiro para poder viajar, escolhei a foto, escolhei a solidão",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 26.86,
      "timestamp_end": 29.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:46:05.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:08.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "bb21e78a-afcc-4c33-9624-fee10e1b0c61",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Comia todas as meninas da cidade de São Paulo e faz de médicos, ou se era com pessoa",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 29.86,
      "timestamp_end": 32.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:46:08.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:11.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "d1c488d2-6713-4aff-b87f-2732d44e3eb9",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Jesus foi mandar pro Econatório, onde aumentou seu adjeto de tanto terror",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 32.86,
      "timestamp_end": 35.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:46:11.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:14.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "38aa5c6f-6126-4f27-8272-625fd637daa1",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Então entendi como a vida funcionava, disse que a iminência por causa dessa classe se movou",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 35.86,
      "timestamp_end": 38.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:46:14.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:17.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "d8c5087f-5f6b-4133-b690-70010685cd4c",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E foi alcançado de tentar, já a escola se comprou uma passagem, foi direto ao salvador",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 38.86,
      "timestamp_end": 40.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:46:17.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:19.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "7409936a-2924-4058-895c-0e332c48ce54",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Ele chegando, foi tomar um padrastrinho, voltou no banheiro e foi falar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 40.86,
      "timestamp_end": 43.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:46:19.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:22.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "a6836e02-8efa-4889-9e74-038bac4eded7",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "O banheiro tinha uma passagem, a pedreira viagem, mas um povo lhe salvava",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 43.86,
      "timestamp_end": 46.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:46:22.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:25.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "98716616-51c3-4571-bcec-5535c1533ea7",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Dizia a ele, estou indo pra Brasília, nesse país o lugar melhor não há",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 46.86,
      "timestamp_end": 49.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:46:25.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:28.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "9e9e10aa-7d7b-4ddb-9f12-c59e7cd6daf8",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Preciso não visitar a minha filha, eu fico aqui e você vai no meu lugar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 49.86,
      "timestamp_end": 52.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:46:28.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:31.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "701ab770-38bc-4037-b62f-7ae4977846ac",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "João assentou sua foce no ônibus e entrou pela nova central",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 52.86,
      "timestamp_end": 54.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:46:31.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:33.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "461755ba-4118-44bd-be8e-a0ee5b3643eb",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Ele ficou enxificado da cidade sanitaria, viado e gostoso de natal",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 54.86,
      "timestamp_end": 57.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T17:46:33.654000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T17:46:36.654000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "e922b598-84a5-4857-903f-b01894476b41",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E o que ousa de cidade linda, no ano novo começa a trabalhar",
      "message_type": "ic",
